raft}} Garden (Nishikyō-ku, Kyoto) - Historic Site, Special Place of Scenic Beauty, and World Heritage Site * {{ill|Nijō Castle|ja|二条城|qq=draft|qq=draft}} Ninomaru Garden ({{ill|Nakagyō-ku, Kyoto|ja|中京区|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, Kyoto) - Historic Site, Special Place of Scenic Beauty, and World Heritage Site * {{ill|Sambō-in Garden|ja|三宝院庭園|qq=draft|qq=draft}} at {{ill|Daigo-ji|ja|醍醐寺|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ({{ill|Fushimi-ku, Kyoto|ja|伏見区|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, Kyoto) - Special Historic Site and Special Place of Scenic Beauty * {{ill|Adachi Museum of Art|ja|足立美術館|qq=draft|qq=draft}} Garden ({{ill|Yasugi|ja|安来市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Shimane Prefecture|ja|島根県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) - Ranked first in a Japanese garden Ranking by the Journal of Japanese Gardening * [[Kōraku-en]] ({{ill|Kita-ku, Okayama|ja|北区 (岡山市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Okayama|ja|岡山市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Okayama Prefecture|ja|岡山県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) - Special Place of Scenic Beauty * {{ill|Ritsurin Garden|ja|栗林公園|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ({{ill|Takamatsu|ja|高松市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Kagawa Prefecture|ja|香川県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) - Special Place of Scenic Beauty * {{ill|Shikina-en|ja|識名園|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ({{ill|Naha|ja|那覇市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Okinawa Prefecture|ja|沖縄県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) - Special Place of Scenic Beauty and World Heritage Site == See Also == * {{ill|Daimyō garden|ja|大名庭園|qq=draft|qq=draft}} * {{ill|Pond Strolling Garden|ja|池泉庭園|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
