京区|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nishikyō-ku, Kyoto|qq=}}, {{ill|Kyoto|ja|京都市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyoto|qq=}}) - Managed by the {{ill|Imperial Household Agency|ja|宮内庁|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Imperial Household Agency|qq=}} * {{ill|Kinkaku-ji|ja|鹿苑寺|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinkaku-ji|qq=}} Garden ({{ill|Kita-ku, Kyoto|ja|北区 (京都市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kita-ku, Kyoto|qq=}}, Kyoto) - Special Historic Site, Special Place of Scenic Beauty, and World Heritage Site * {{ill|Ginkaku-ji|ja|慈照寺|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ginkaku-ji|qq=}} Garden ({{ill|Sakyō-ku, Kyoto|ja|左京区|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sakyō-ku, Kyoto|qq=}}, Kyoto) - Special Historic Site, Special Place of Scenic Beauty, and World Heritage Site * {{ill|Tenryū-ji|ja|天龍寺|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenryū-ji|qq=}} Garden ({{ill|Ukyō-ku, Kyoto|ja|右京区|1=Ukyō-ku, Kyoto|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ukyō-ku, Kyoto|13=User:Immanuelle/Ukyō-ku, Kyoto|qq=}}, Kyoto) - Historic Site, Special Place of Scenic Beauty, and World Heritage Site * {{ill|Saihō-ji (Kyoto)|ja|西芳寺|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Saihō-ji (Kyoto)|qq=}} Garden (Nishikyō-ku, Kyoto) - Historic Site, Special Place of Scenic Beauty, and World Heritage Site * {{ill|Nijō Castle|ja|二条城|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nijō Castle|qq=}} Ninomaru Garden ({{ill|Nakagyō-ku, Kyoto|ja|中京区|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nakagyō-ku, Kyoto|qq=}}, Kyoto) - Historic Site, Special Place of Scenic Beauty, and World Heritage Site * {{ill|Sambō-in Garden|ja|三宝院庭園|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sambō-in Garden|qq=}} at {{ill|Daigo-ji|ja|醍醐寺|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Daigo-ji|qq=}} ({{ill|Fushimi-ku, Kyoto|ja|伏見区|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fushimi-ku, Kyoto|qq=}}, Kyoto) - Special Historic Site and Special Place of Scenic Beauty * {{ill|Adachi Museum of Art|ja|足立美術館|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Adachi Museum of Art|qq=}} Garden ({{ill|Yasugi|ja|安来市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yasugi|qq=}}, {{ill|Shimane Prefecture|ja|島根県|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shimane Prefecture|qq=}}) - Ranked first in a Japanese garden Ranking by the Journal of Japanese Gardening * [[Kōraku-en]] ({{ill|Kita-ku, Okayama|ja|北区 (岡山市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kita-ku, Okayama|qq=}}, {{ill|Okayama|ja|岡山市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Okayama|qq=}}, {{ill|Okayama Prefecture|ja|岡山県|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Okayama Prefecture|qq=}}) - Special Place of Scenic Beauty * {{ill|Ritsurin Garden|ja|栗林公園|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ritsurin Garden|qq=}} ({{ill|Takamatsu|ja|高松市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takamatsu|qq=}}, {{ill|Kagawa Prefecture|ja|香川県|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kagawa Prefecture|qq=}}) - Special Place of Scenic Beauty * {{ill|Shikina-en|ja|識名園|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shikina-en|qq=}} ({{ill|Naha|ja|那覇市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Naha|qq=}}, {{ill|Okinawa Prefecture|ja|沖縄県|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Okinawa Prefecture|qq=}}) - Special Place of Scenic Beauty and World Heritage Site == See Also == * {{ill|Daimyō garden|ja|大名庭園|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Daimyō garden|qq=}} * {{ill|Pond Strolling Garden|ja|池泉庭園|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Pond Strolling Garden|qq=}}
